Project Overview
The Organization Project Login Page is a web-based application designed to facilitate project management within organizations. It provides a secure login system for users to access project details, create new projects, and update existing project information.

Key Features
User Authentication: Users can log in securely using their project ID and password.
Project Details: Users can fetch detailed information about specific projects from the database.
Create New Projects: Authorized users can create new projects by providing necessary details.
Update Project Details: Users can modify project information as needed.

Why it's Useful
Streamlined Project Management: The system centralizes project information, making it easier for team members to access and update project details.
Enhanced Security: By requiring authentication, the system ensures that only authorized users can view and modify project information.
Improved Collaboration: With access to up-to-date project details, team members can collaborate more effectively and stay aligned on project goals.
